%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as JIRA Linked WBS UI
participant BFF as Execution BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant JIRA as JIRA Sync Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open JIRA-linked milestone
UI->>BFF: Load JIRA-synced WBS
BFF->>ORCH: Get read-only JIRA WBS view
ORCH->>JIRA: Fetch synced JIRA hierarchy
JIRA->>READDB: Query JIRA workspace and synced JIRA items
READDB-->>JIRA: Synced JIRA rows
JIRA-->>ORCH: Read-only JIRA WBS
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show JIRA WBS in read-only format